These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
House: wooden, ranch-style, farmhouse, modern
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, yellow, green, amber
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, videographer, musician
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 2. the wooden house is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the modern house##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 6. the dressmaker is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the mexican is the farmhouse house##1
 8. the videographer is in an even position##4
 9. the dressmaker is between the musician and the person who likes amber##2
10. the wooden house is the musician##1
11. the person who likes green is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| House          | farmhouse  | wooden    | modern    | ranch-style   |
| Color   | yellow     | ebony   | green       | amber    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Job           | engineer | musician       | dressmaker | videographer     |

