.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, march, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, country, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, apricot, ivory, amber
 1. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is the colombian##1
 5. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday          | september  | august    | march     | april       |
| Music-Genre         | country | gospel | soul   | d&b |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| Color         | ivory | amber  | azure | apricot   |

