.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, orchid, azalea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat, dannemann, prince
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, brown, black, chestnut
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 2. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is the prince-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the person who likes emerald is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Flower           | orchid | iris | marigold | azalea     |
| Cigar   | baccarat      | prince   | fonseca   | dannemann |
| Color           | chestnut         | emerald       | black  | brown       |

