.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, billiard, mah-jongg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, bluemaster, dunhill
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, roller, snowmobile, taxi
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person playing domino is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the roller##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person playing billiard is the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | billiard   | domino   | scrabble   |
| Cigar       | baccarat        | dunhill | old-henry    | bluemaster       |
| Transport      | taxi | roller    | snowmobile  | tram |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

