.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, r&b, metal
House: art-deco, farmhouse, wooden, palace
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, motorbike, van
 1. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the wooden house is between the person driving the skateboard and the fan of metal##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the librarian is the fan of jazz##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
 7. the fan of salsa is the bartender##1
 8. the wooden house is the librarian##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the palace house##1
11. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
12. the palace house is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Music-Genre    | r&b    | metal      | jazz          | salsa    |
| House   | farmhouse | palace       | wooden | art-deco |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Transport   | bike   | van | motorbike        | skateboard   |

