 5. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
