 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the librarian is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
