.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, japanese, malaysian, american
House: craftsman, tower, cape-cod, futuristic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bolivar, fonseca, siglo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the american##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 7. the tower house is on the far right##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
11. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the craftsman house is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality      | malaysian       | japanese | polish        | american        |
| House         | futuristic | cape-cod       | craftsman | tower |
| Cigar   | siglo     | bolivar        | tiparillo    | fonseca      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

