.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, ferret, horse
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, black, white, ivory
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, baking, puzzles, hiking
 1. the owner of the horse is the person who likes white##1
 2. the person who likes white is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes black##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet   | goldfish      | frog | horse     | ferret        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Color         | black    | lilac | white      | ivory |
| Hobby     | hiking | baking     | puzzles | skydiving       |

 